.TP
.BR charon.cisco_unity " [no]
Send Cisco Unity vendor ID payload (IKEv1 only)
.TP
.BR charon.close_ike_on_child_failure " [no]"
Close the IKE_SA if setup of the CHILD_SA along with IKE_AUTH failed
.TP
